title: Please vaccinate your kids!
description:
Doctors all around the world agree that there's no reason not to get your children vaccinated. Doing so will not only protect your children from terrible diseases but will also help protect all the other children in the community. Scientific research has always shown that vaccines are very benefical without any major downsides.

More information about the safety of vaccines: https://www.cdc.gov/vaccinesafety/concerns/autism.html

Special thanks to VoiceoverPete for being part of this video: https://www.youtube.com/user/PremIntel

And thanks to the other actors from Fiverr, listed in order of appearance.
